{"tid":2367542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"研究：貿易戰使美國損失24.5萬個職位 損失慘重","createTime":"2021-01-15T12:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T11:10:19.000Z","uid":199670,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea01dd22600282c4950345fe719aaa16b4cd25f4","tid":2367542,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"美中貿易全國委員會（USCBC）調查結果顯示，中美兩國貿易戰導致達24.5萬個美國職位流失。倘雙方逐步取消關稅措施，將促進經濟增長，料在2025年前為美國帶來14.5萬個新工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述USCBC調查估計，美國對中國的出口為美國提供120萬個就業機會，中國的跨國公司直接僱用197,000名美國人，而美國公司在2019年在中國的投資為1,050億美元。<br />\n<br />\n不過，如果雙方貿易關係進一步惡化，最壞情況下，在未來5年內將使美國GDP減少1.6萬億美元，更可導致2022年美國就業人數減少73.2萬個，到2025年減少32萬個就業機會。"},{"pid":"63341d8d45619bffe5528d630dc4d0ff6eaa00de","tid":2367542,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">川普稱貿易戰「好打易贏」 何以中國最終勝出</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E5%A5%BD%E6%89%93%E6%98%93%E8%B4%8F-%E4%BD%86%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E5%8B%9D%E5%87%BA-022519567.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2598%2593%25E8%25B4%258F-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2587%25BA-022519567.html&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=7bb5df70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0-%E5%A5%BD%E6%89%93%E6%98%93%E8%B4%8F-%E4%BD%86%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E7%B5%82%E5%8B%9D%E5%87%BA-022519567.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb408ff2093a1ad6e2b4a6a06af0430074cd6603","tid":2367542,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15